.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/israeli-army-used-advanced-robots-supplied-by-mossad-for-combat-in-gaza-tunnels/0000018f-3824-d516-afbf-fee630230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对加沙战争的学生抗议者在哪里？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/where-are-israels-student-protesters-against-the-gaza-war/0000018f-34e7-d0b5-a59f-35e7619c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/where-are-israels-student-protesters-against-the-gaza-war/0000018f-34e7-d0b5-a59f-35e7619c0000</guid></item><item><title>你口袋里的 BDS：新应用程序促进抵制在以色列运营的公司</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bds-in-your-pocket-new-app-promotes-boycott-of-companies-operating-in-israel/0000018f-3410-d0b5-a59f-35d575a00000</link><description>该应用程序“不，谢谢”帮助消费者识别与以色列有联系的全球品牌，尽管一场反攻势已确保该产品在 Google Play 和苹果应用商店上的评分陷入困境</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:04:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bds-in-your-pocket-new-app-promotes-boycott-of-companies-operating-in-israel/0000018f-3410-d0b5-a59f-35d575a00000</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯和美国希望达成共同防御协议——无论有没有以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-and-the-u-s-want-a-mutual-defense-pact-with-or-without-israel/0000018f-3658-d8fb-a1df-bf7e2e460000</link><description>华盛顿和利雅得担心正常化协议的第三方会以政治利益的名义危及他们的安全利益，因此他们正在制定一项应急计划，根据该计划，双边合作不依赖于以色列与沙特的正常化</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-and-the-u-s-want-a-mutual-defense-pact-with-or-without-israel/0000018f-3658-d8fb-a1df-bf7e2e460000</guid></item><item><title>报告：哈马斯对以色列最新停火提议持“负面”态度，但谈判将继续</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-li