2024-05-01/ty-article/.highlight/columbias-entitled-squatters-and-the-manhattan-version-of-air-dropped-aid/0000018f-353b-d8fb-a1df-bd7fd4420000</guid></item><item><title>“对于一些犹太人来说，围绕加沙的校园战争很糟糕。但它们并不是暴力、反犹太主义的噩梦”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-01/ty-article-podcast/for-jews-campus-wars-over-gaza-suck-but-theyre-not-a-violent-antisemitic-nightmare/0000018f-34c2-d0b5-a59f-35c7d90d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:42:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-01/ty-article-podcast/for-jews-campus-wars-over-gaza-suck-but-theyre-not-a-violent-antisemitic-nightmare/0000018f-34c2-d0b5-a59f-35c7d90d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 208 天：布林肯表示拉法行动将减少人质交易的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-208-blinken-says-rafah-op-will-diminish-chances-of-hostage-deal/0000018f-3500-d444-ab9f-f50f5a690001</link><description>布林肯在以色列会见内塔尼亚胡总理，称哈马斯是停火/人质释放协议无法达成的唯一原因 ■ 以色列代表团抵达开罗继续停火谈判 ■ 据报道，埃及停火提案的措辞不包括以色列的承诺不要返回加沙 ■ 约旦官方媒体报道，以色列定居者袭击了两支前往加沙的援助车队 ■ 战争进入 208 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-208-blinken-says-rafah-op-will-diminish-chances-of-hostage-deal/0000018f-3500-d444-ab9f-f50f5a690001</guid></item><item><title>美国联合航空表示 5 月 9 日前飞往特拉维夫的航班已取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/united-airlines-says-flights-to-tel-aviv-are-cancelled-up-to-may-9/0000018f-3492-d8c4-afef-3dfe63ed0000</link><description>由于以色列和伊朗袭击事件后的安全担忧，该航空公司取消了 5 月 2 日之前飞往以色列的航班，并已将航班延期一周，以完成安全评估</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/united-airlines-says-flights-to-tel-aviv-are-cancelled-up-to-may-9/0000018f-3492-d8c4-afef-3dfe63ed0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列与哈马斯协议的乐观情绪减弱，针对拉法的行动可能会导致人质丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/optimism-wanes-over-israel-hamas-deal-and-a-move-on-rafah-could-cost-hostages-lives/0000018f-33f3-d9c3-abcf-7bf7d07e0000</link><description>尽管调解人担心哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔会拒绝埃及的提议，但以色列极右翼部长们却力图阻止任何协议。 ■ 尽管国际社会反对，行动上也遇到困难，内塔尼亚胡仍坚持主张拉法入侵，冒着人质、士兵和平民遭受损失的风险</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/optimism-wanes-over-israel-hamas-deal-and-a-move-on-rafah-could-cost-hostages-lives/0000018f-33f3-d9c3-abcf-7bf7d07e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队削减守卫约旦河西岸定居点的士兵人数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-slashes-number-of-soldiers-guarding-west-bank-settlements/0000018f-3455-dbd5-a7df-fef7a7350000</link><description>战争爆发后，戒备状态下的士兵人数达到8000人，随后逐渐减少，目前只剩下1000人。这一削减是与定居点协调进行的，允许更多的定居者携带武器</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-slashes-number-of-soldiers-guarding-west-bank-settlements/0000018f-3455-dbd5-a7df-fef7a7350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院驳回被监禁的巴勒斯坦人巴尔古提对监禁条款的上诉，援引哈马斯合作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-rejects-barghouti-appeal-on-imprisonment-terms-cites-hamas-collaboration/0000018f-3438-d9c3-abcf-7e7d34760000</link><description>过去几个月一直被单独监禁的法塔赫高级官员声称，他没有获得基本设备。法院表示，Marwan Barghouti 的请愿书忽略了自 10 月 7 日以来安全囚犯条款的变化</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-rejects-barghouti-appeal-on-imprisonment-terms-cites-hamas-collaboration/0000018f-3438-d9c3-abcf-7e7d34760000</guid></item><item><title>美国终于找到了对以色列和内塔尼亚胡的有效影响力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/america-has-finally-found-effective-leverage-on-israel-and-netanyahu/0000018f-339c-d8fb-a1df-bffe7d110000</link><description>即使国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗尚未对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和其他以色列高级官员发出逮捕令，其影响也已经在加沙和人质谈判中显现出来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/america-has-finally-found-effective-leverage-on-israel-and-netanyahu/0000018f-339c-d8fb-a1df-bffe7d110000</guid></item></channel></rss>